@startuml de1ux_statlord

actor User
participant "Dashboard Editor" as Editor
participant "Redux Store" as Store
participant "API Client" as APIClient
participant "Backend API" as API
database "Database" as DB
participant "Display Viewer" as Viewer

User -> Editor: Create/Edit Dashboard
Editor -> Store: Update Layout State
Store -> Editor: Reflect Changes

User -> Editor: Save Dashboard
Editor -> APIClient: Save Layout
APIClient -> API: POST /layouts
API -> DB: Store Layout
DB --> API: Confirm Storage
API --> APIClient: Success Response
APIClient --> Editor: Update Confirmation

User -> Viewer: View Dashboard
Viewer -> APIClient: Fetch Layout
APIClient -> API: GET /layouts/{id}
API -> DB: Retrieve Layout
DB --> API: Layout Data
API --> APIClient: Layout JSON
APIClient --> Viewer: Layout Data
Viewer -> Viewer: Render Dashboard

loop Data Update
    APIClient -> API: GET /gauges
    API -> DB: Fetch Updated Data
    DB --> API: Latest Data
    API --> APIClient: Updated Gauge Data
    APIClient -> Store: Update Gauge State
    Store -> Viewer: Reflect Data Changes
end

@enduml